thread.title: Nadiah Abuleela
thread.title_full: Rush Hair and Beauty reviewed by Nadiah Abuleela

author: Nadiah Abuleela
title: Nadiah Abuleela
text: This was my third visit to Rush Liverpool, I can't speak highly enough of the staff, courteous and friendly and make me feel extremely comfortable. I'm looking forward to my next appointment already and I only visited yesterday! My hair is the best it's been in a very long time. My Rush blend ombré is exceptional! ❤️❤️❤️
